otocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 30190031, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/93.0.4556.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1933.709, "format": "dash-4383151095250071v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by ufocaller", "description": "Reupload for the new translation on instagram 🐚 \n\nThis is not just about harmony.\nThis is about not being able to see the ordinary (our spiritual perception is being blocked) \n\n12 represents completion, closure, a box that can be sealed. 13 is the one beyond: the spiral, the continuation, the opening into transformation. Where 12 locks the system, 13 cracks it open.\n \nWhen 13 is erased, we lose the code that points us past appearances. We lose the instinct to question, to transform, to step into the unseen. We are kept looping inside completion instead of leaping into evolution.\n\nBringing 13 back means reclaiming the ability to see what has been hidden in plain sight. It’s saying: “I refuse the box. I choose the spiral.”\n\n#number13 #naturaltime #13mooncalendar #spiritualunderstanding #spiritualbeings #spiritualgrowth", "duration": 124.9, "timestamp": 1767966931, "uploader_id": "209669707", "uploader": "UFO 🧚‍♀️", "channel": "ufocaller", "like_count": 67181, "comment_count": 2657, "comments": [{"author": "akj18722", "author_id": "75811504914", "id": "18460479298099800", "text": "Friday the 13th! My favorite day!", "timestamp": 1775517820}, {"author": "borisfusman", "author_id": "1557579775", "id": "18587770279002396", "text": "Just saying 13=1 in gimatria in Hebrew. Meaning the word for 1 is ehad(אחד). And 13+13=26 and that is the full gods name י' ה' ו' ה. I right it separately because I didn't want to use the name for nothing. So it not a coincidence, it's for perpeuse ❤️", "timestamp": 1775508020}, {"author": "edw333r", "author_id": "3571162013", "id": "18065266814465298", "text": "😍😍😍", "timestamp": 1775500933}, {"author": "api_olea5", "author_id": "2315052050", "id": "18077055578385672", "text": "Pretty", "timestamp": 1775487856}, {"author": "kittyskates13", "author_id": "77439170720", "id": "17854717326690561", "text": "13 is my lucky / favorite number", "timestamp": 1775481635}, {"author": "sacredhealing_scarlettpadilla", "author_id": "78040352878", "id": "18110138176836140", "text": "They gave me a flight seat number 13 and I just wished I would’ve gone to another dimention 🤣", "timestamp": 1775480873}, {"author": "angelina_markou_", "author_id": "3817414622", "id": "17944113861029086", "text": "Thank you about this but what about times before moon was on our sky? There are some ancient writings from ancient Arcadians in Greece one of the first civilisation existed that speak about time before moon and after moon", "timestamp": 1775479940}, {"author": "cj_cichlids", "author_id": "1507618381", "id": "18083621318201462", "text": "❤️❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1775471804}, {"author": "niecy81", "author_id": "45523683", "id": "17942226426161153", "text": "Before knowing all this I was drawn to the number 13 already. I used to play basketball as a teenager. I wanted the number 13 on my shirt. Kept it all through the years. It's my lucky number.", "timestamp": 1775463720}, {"author": "ivan_ochoa70", "author_id": "57932609301", "id": "18047299415756000", "text": "13, Mientras más me mamas, más me crece", "timestamp": 1775455338}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/612119139_18551662039005708_6434217458925320477_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p640x640_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4zMzc1eDYwMDAuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdn